%N A169934 Number of permutations of [n] with the number moved left exceeding the number moved right by 2.
%H A169934 Seiichi Manyama, <a href="/A169934/b169934.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..450</a>
%F A169934 a(n) = Sum_{e=0..floor((n+2)/2)} binomial(n,2*e-2) * A271697(2*e-2,e). - _Seiichi Manyama_, Apr 23 2026
%o A169934 (PARI) E(n, k) = sum(j=0, k, (-1)^j*binomial(n+1, j)*(k+1-j)^n);
%o A169934 a271697(n, k) = sum(j=0, n, (-1)^(n-j)*binomial(n, j)*E(j, k));
%o A169934 a(n) = sum(e=0, (n+2)\2, binomial(n, 2*e-2)*a271697(2*e-2, e)); \\ _Seiichi Manyama_, Apr 23 2026
